	Every industry requires its own customized software which meets its needs. Eg. the software used in pharmacies. Even a bus conductor gives a printed ticket, everything is programmed.
	Hence the job opportunities for software engineers and programmers are high.
	<br><br>
	We live in an era of technology ... People brush their teetch after checking their whatsapp messages. We may forget to pay the electricity bill but never forget to check our facebook account.
	Just as there are questions there are textbooks for everything. All the great technologies are inpired from the needs, requirements and ideas. Need is the mother of all inventions.
	<br><br>
	This is just the beginning, there is much more to come, one of the recent rends for today is cloud computing. It means that all our inmformation will be stored on some distant computer as if we were actually in that place, and the same file could be accessed by many people at the same time.
	All great things start very small, all big companies have very humble beginnings.
