 Facebook was started by Mark Zuckerburg in his college dorm room, Apple was started by Steve Jobs and Steve Wozniak in a a garage.
 There are more stories to tell, but everything has its time to shine ... as well as wither away. 10 years back Orkut was something new, then people turned to facebook, now it is whatsapp time.
 In the race to survival the only technology which lives is the one which adapts by learning from its mistake.
<br><br>
 Software is like fashion, it changes but never stops. Right now if feel a small boy standing in front of a candy store with a two rupee coin in his hand. I can see so many candies and sweets.
 The internet, this computer world and everything else which has charge and data flowing through it is at the center of my admiration, i feel it, and i am happy to be a part of it. 
